HEADWORD: Exquisitely
<hw>Ex"qui*site*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In an exquisite manner or
degree; <as>as, lace <ex>exquisitely</ex> wrought</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>To a sensitive observer there was something <qex>exquisitely</qex>
painful in it.</q> <rj><qau>Hawthorne.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Exquisiteness</ent>⟦br⟧
